      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or scratches. Every trim piece, weather seal, and glass panel is in factory-original condition. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, fitted with a fresh set of premium performance tires. Moving inside, the interior is a time capsule. The leather seats remain firm and supple with no signs of bolster wear, fading, or creasing. All technology interfaces, buttons, and switches function with tactile precision, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since purchase. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. The vehicle comes with a complete, documented service history from an authorized dealer, showing proactive maintenance well ahead of factory recommendations. There are no mechanical leaks, no unusual noises, and the transmission shifts with seamless accuracy. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
